message.body: Yeah I am, but I'm still functioning so it's not bad. I'm just tired all the time. I'm actually at the mall buying my sister a bday gift.
Aw, that's good, do you know what you're getting?
Foundation. It had a starter kit with a primer, finishing powder, and full size foundation. So technically it was a steal.
Oh yea. The foundation alone is like forty-something dollars. Some brush though!
I know right? Craziness. Yeah the foundation alone was $42. Whatevs. She got her color matched so there's no fear that it'll be wrong.
Yea, it's a good foundation. I have the HD one which I think is the same one you bought. Lasts a while too.
Oh that's great to know....since I bought one too.
Are you going to be coming out tonight?
Yeah. I think the grand total of my purchase today was a whopping $360. But I was going to go if you guys weren't going to lucys. I know that I won't make it till 2-3am.
Whoa!! Damn Jen, makin' it rain at Sephora!
Oh okay. Yea, we're actually not going to Lucy's. Going to another bar. Understandable, maybe next time, get some caffeine in those veins ;)
Oh what one are you going to?
Oh sounds fun. Haha. I hope you guys have tons of fun!!
Thank you!!! Hope you feel better :)
